com.norbl.cbp.ppe.gui.networkspec
Interface ChoiceComponent

All Known Implementing Classes:
LabeledTextFieldCC, OtherCC, RadioButtonCC, SpotPriceCC
public interface ChoiceComponent

A JComponent used to specify a choice. Every Choice creates an appropriate ChoiceComponent but a Choice can supply other information as well (such as a description).

A ChoiceComponent is either a JPanel or something (like a JRadioButton that can go into JPanel. Non-JPanel choice componts are usually displayed in a ChoiceSet, which extends JPanel.
